It's better if the date is just simply there.

278
00:26:24,319 --> 00:26:28,019
黙って引っ張ったりしないでよ
Don't pull on it silently.

279
00:26:28,019 --> 00:26:31,319
不格好な蝶にしないでよ
Don't turn it into a misshapen butterfly.

280
00:26:31,319 --> 00:26:34,019
結んだつもりが ほどいてたり
Thinking we tied it, we were untying it,

281
00:26:34,019 --> 00:26:38,819
