We probably just don't match.

345
00:32:41,864 --> 00:32:45,464
二人きりしかいない部屋でさ
In a room with just the two of us,

346
00:32:45,664 --> 00:32:48,964
貴方ばっかり話していたよね
you were the only one talking, weren't you?

347
00:32:49,264 --> 00:32:54,564
もしいつか何処かで会えたら
If we happen to meet somewhere again someday,

348
00:32:54,964 --> 00:33:00,464
